{
  "stem": "232.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I don't know what they, they could find out from refugees.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this is how they went into France as spies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we came to this village.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were some, some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Belgian officers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And right away, they went to the French authorities there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they said, we are Belge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there are a lot of Jews here, refugees from, from other countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so, so they separated already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In France, the, the, the Christian people were taken care of from the government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took care of us, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The first few weeks, they put us in hotels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were-- we were fed by the hotels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the hotels, we were fed and taken care of.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And after a little while, it was-- we, we arrived there May 10, May 18-- it was almost in the end of May.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in June-- in June, the French army capitulated.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It meant that France is occupied, will be occupied by Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Here we are, in a little village in the end of the-- of the tracks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we hear the Germans occupied France.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then it became part Vichy, part German occupation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So luckily, we were in the Vichy part of France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were in Luchon about two or three months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was no radio communications.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But they gave out flyers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in the littler streets in the village, came a man with a drum.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he went from street to street drumming, and shouting out, announcement!",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Avis!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Avis!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This means 'announcement.' And then he came, 'The government of France, the, the authorities of Luchon, requires that all the Jews have to come to this place and present themselves.' OK.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in this village.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
